==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: If you don't read for three days, you will become unattractive.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: sān rì bù dú shū, mìan mù kĕ zēng

===Phrase===
'''[[三]][[日]][[不]][[读书]]，[[面目可憎]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') If you are not diligent in your studies, you will remain ignorant, and nobody will be attracted to you.

===Alternate forms===
[[三]][[日]][[不]][[讀書]]，[[面目可憎]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

